      <hedline>
        <hl1>Correction</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction; Jan 7 review of Chris Hedges book American Fascists: The Christian Right and the War on America referred incorrectly to American Veterans in Domestic Defense</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>A review on Jan. 7 about ''American Fascists: The Christian Right and the War on America,'' by Chris Hedges, referred incorrectly to American Veterans in Domestic Defense, a group that conducted a traveling exhibit of a Ten Commandments monument banned from the judicial building in Montgomery, Ala. The group and its tour are in fact mentioned in the book.</p>
      </block>
